author: sussman
msg: Hm.  Funny.  trans_tests.py #2 has been failing for weeks.  But get
this -- 'make check' NEVER RUNS the script!  Good thing Pilchie
decided to run trans_tests.py by hand.
* build.conf (paths):  duh.  add trans_tests.py to the list of tests.
* trans_tests.py (update_modified_with_translation):  expect a "C"
status code instead of "G" status code.  Once we switched 'svn up'
to start using diff3 a few weeks ago, the results of this test
became more detailed and correct.  The conflict markers should be
expected, as well as the conflict backup files.
* svn_version.h (SVN_VER_MINOR):  bump to 0.11.1
